<i>adverb</i>: 당돌히 [당ː돌히] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>당돌히 [당ː돌히]</dt><br>
<dd>1. daringly; bravely</dd><br>
<dd>겁내거나 어려워하지 않고 당당하게.</dd><br>
<dd>Confidently without feeling scared or uncomfortable.</dd><br>
<dd>2. insolently; rudely</dd><br>
<dd>윗사람에게 하는 말이나 행동이 주제넘고 버릇이 없게.</dd><br>
<dd>With an impolite and impudent attitude in speaking to or behaving toward one's elder or superior.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>